        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>canapés (elegant sofas) [300038636], sofas [300038634], multiple-seating furniture [300038493], seating furniture [300037769], furniture by form or function [300048628], furniture [300037680], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to S-shaped sofas with ends curving inward so two people could sit face to face. For straight-fronted sofas with small triangular seats (sometimes detachable) set outside the arms at either end, use "confidantes."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Úsese para sofás con forma de S con extremos que se curvan hacia adentro para que la gente pueda sentarse cara a cara. Para sofás con el frente recto con pequeños asientos triangulares (algunas veces desmontables) colocados por fuera de los brazos en cada extremo, use "confident."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor sofa's met een S-vorm waarbij de uiteinden naar binnen zijn gebogen zodat twee mensen met hun gezicht naar elkaar toe kunnen zitten. Gebruik 'confidentes' voor sofa's met een rechte voorkant en kleine, driehoekige zittingen die soms afneembaar zijn en aan de buitenzijden van de armleuningen zitten.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>S-förmiges Sofa mit nach innen gebogenen Enden, so dass sich zwei Personen gegenüber sitzen können. Für gerade Sofas mit kleinen dreieckigen Sitzen (manchmal abnehmbar), die sich außerhalb der Armlehnen an beiden Enden anschließen, benutze "Canapé à confidents".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>S型的沙發，兩端朝內側彎曲，可以讓兩個人面對面地坐著。若是指稱椅座正面平直，扶手兩側附加可拆式或固定之小型三角椅座的沙發，使用「密友沙發」(confidantes)一詞。
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
